com.iopipe

Class CustomMetric

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iopipe.CustomMetric
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<CustomMetric>

    public final class CustomMetric
extends Object
implements Comparable<CustomMetric>
    This represents a custom metric which may have a string or long value, these may be used to add extra data points that are normally not present. Custom metric names are limited to the length specified in IOpipeConstants.NAME_CODEPOINT_LIMIT.
    Since:
    2018/01/20
